{
  "api": "Primetric REST API v1 (https://developer.primetric.com/)",
  "docs": "https://developer.primetric.com/",
  "reviewed_at": "2026-07-03",
  "scope": "wave2 fan-out migration: the 4 legacy-parity read streams only (employees, projects, clients, roles). Primetric's write/mutation endpoints (project/employee assignment, time-off requests, etc.) are out of scope; legacy itself ships no writes (capabilities.write is false).",
